---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../styles/pages.css';
---

<Base title="Contact" titleZh="联系" description="Contact QuasarG about Taste Bank and front-end style systems." wide>
  <main class="subpage contact-page">
    <header class="contact-page-top">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span data-ui-en>Contact</span><span data-ui-zh>联系</span></p>
      <h1><span data-ui-en>Add a taste.<br />Build something distinct.</span><span class="cn-page-title" data-ui-zh>贡献一种品味，<br />创造独特界面。</span></h1>
      <p><span data-ui-en>For a new style pack, a front-end collaboration, or questions about using Taste Bank, find me on GitHub.</span><span data-ui-zh>提交新的风格包、发起前端协作，或交流 Taste Bank 的使用方式，请通过 GitHub 联系我。</span></p>
    </header>
    <a class="contact-page-handle" href="https://github.com/QuasarG" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">QuasarG <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
    <footer class="contact-page-foot"><span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} QuasarG</span><span><span data-ui-en>Code-ready visual systems</span><span data-ui-zh>可直接编码的视觉系统</span></span><span>Taste Bank</span></footer>
  </main>
</Base>
